      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The data was processed by MS-DIAL (version 4.38)... An in-house MS/MS library containing 449 and 172 plastic-related chemicals in the positive and negative modes, respectively, was built... we developed a R package, mspcompiler, to clean and compile various MS/MS libraries for identification in MS-DIAL.",
