    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/smiles-structure-annotation-from-molfiles/008",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The data was processed by MS-DIAL (version 4.38) with a mass tolerance of 0.01 and 0.025 Da for MS1 and MS2, respectively... An R package, namely, mspcompiler, was developed to compile various publicly accessible and in-house MS/MS libraries. The library was then utilized for identification in MS-DIAL.",
